OL,3,CAmbulance workers vote to strike in
OL,4,Cresponse to proposed new shift system
OL,6,FAmbulance workers and paramedics have
OL,7,Fvoted 'overwhelmingly' for industrial
OL,8,Faction in reponse to management
OL,9,Fproposals to impose a new shift system.
OL,11,FThe ballot was closed with 86% of
OL,12,Fmembers in the Unite union who voted
OL,13,Ffor the industrial action following
OL,14,Fthe annoucement of a pilot scheme to
OL,15,Fbegin in the South Eastern trust.
OL,17,FThe union said the proposals risk
OL,18,Fleaving areas without ambulance cover
OL,19,Facross Northern Ireland.
