OL,3,CAmbulance workers vote to strike in
OL,4,Cresponse to proposed new shift system
OL,6,FExisting NIAS cover require ambulances
OL,7,Fto travel long distances to cover low-
OL,8,Fstaffed areas but Unite have said this
OL,9,Fwill increase the likelihood for such
OL,10,Flong journeys and leave other areas,
OL,11,Fespecially rural ones, with
OL,12,Finsufficient cover.
OL,14,FSharon Graham, Unite general secretary
OL,15,Fsaid: "These new shifts are just a
OL,16,Fbandage to cover over the ambulance
OL,17,Fservice staffing crisis.
OL,19,F"Ambulance workers will not pay the
OL,20,Fprice for a crisis they didn't cause."
